          `minSqrtPrice: ${minSqrtPrice}\n` +
          `maxSqrtPrice: ${maxSqrtPrice}\n` +
          `sqrtPrice: ${sqrtPrice}\n\n` +
          `The pool state might be corrupted or incomplete.`
        );
